# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# __floordiv__ dict-presence — operator.contains(Cls.__dict__, '__floordiv__')
#
# All 14 asyncio classes return false for __floordiv__.
# No asyncio type defines floor division.
# asyncio.Task/Future: result containers; task // task is not defined.
# asyncio.Queue: queue // n has no defined meaning.
# asyncio.Semaphore/Lock/Condition/BoundedSemaphore: acquire/release-based
#   primitives; floor division is semantically inapplicable.
# asyncio.Handle/TimerHandle: callback objects; no floor division.
# asyncio.Timeout: a deadline guard; no floor division of deadlines.
# asyncio.TaskGroup: a structured-concurrency scope; no floor division.
# asyncio.StreamReader/StreamWriter: I/O objects; no floor division.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

